                     desc limit 1) as most_common_source_name, (select most_common_value from user_variables where variable_id=5985049 and most_common_value is not NULL group by most_common_value order by count(most_common_value)
                     desc limit 1) as most_common_value, (select most_common_value from user_variables where variable_id=5985049 and most_common_value is not NULL group by most_common_value order by count(most_common_value)
